{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1525999, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 300528, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "额，当然是linux啊", "timestamp": 1619339200, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1526015, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 300528, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "win\n1. 因为有WSL，所以用Windows就事用Linux（\n2. mac买不起，黑苹果还是别想了，弄到能用都很难\n3. 用Windows意味着当你想做一件事的时候根本没软件可用的概率最低", "timestamp": 1619339349, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1526027, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 300528, "reply_to": 1526015, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 有理", "timestamp": 1619339470, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1526030, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 300528, "reply_to": 1526015, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: cs专业不太会遇到这个情况，所以mac可以一战。电子啥的话没win分分钟暴毙", "timestamp": 1619339478, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1526046, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 300528, "reply_to": 1526030, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 像我平时各种事都做一点，又是编程又是剪视频又是打游戏的就还是得win\n另外贵系软院都有数电课，那些软件也还是得用（", "timestamp": 1619339564, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1526177, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 300528, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "win,你买mac打什么游戏？不会吧不会吧，不会有CS专业的人真的不打游戏吧（x）好吧确实有，如果不打游戏或者是主机党那mac挺好。打pc游戏的话就别想mac了", "timestamp": 1619340650, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1526422, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 300528, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "1:1，这惊人的比例", "timestamp": 1619342476, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1526857, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 300528, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "认真分析，如果只能有一个系统的话，还是win，因为mac不太能显卡机器学习。除了这个原因，mac体验良好。\n当然可以双系统保平安，但我已经双系统win+mac了，三系统不太想折腾电脑了。\n另外，如果有正经显卡需求的话，实验室会提供算力的，另外google colab等地方也有免费的算力薅（但是便利性还是及不上本地）\nmac的优势在于丝滑的使用体验（包括命令行），但预算吃紧也许不是值得换取的。", "timestamp": 1619346068, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1526868, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 300528, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "顺便安利imac，不要以为他是mac系统不能玩游戏，装个win双系统，独显起码能应付一波大作", "timestamp": 1619346157, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1526939, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 300528, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : 当然是Linux", "timestamp": 1619346704, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1527296, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 300528, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "iPhone macbook ipad 台式机黑苹果/windows双系统。同一套🍎生态用起来会很舒服，特别是mac对高分辨率的支持比windows好太多了，linux要用的mac基本都没问题，除了N卡驱动会难受一点点、黑苹果安装需要折腾一两天之外没有什么稳定性上的缺点。windows就只用来打游戏", "timestamp": 1619349296, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1527326, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 300528, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "icloud开200g的套餐，然后把要同步的东西都放上去，配一下zotero的同步，看文献就可以多终端同步了。然后显卡驱动其实无所谓，因为跑代码都有实验室服务器呢，终端配好就行了。尤其是mac的iterm，可玩性还是不错的", "timestamp": 1619349504, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1527332, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 300528, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "另外很多steam游戏其实也有mac版，hans常玩的几个游戏也能在mac上运行", "timestamp": 1619349560, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 300528, "reply": 13, "tag": null, "text": "#300521\nCS专业，哪个更好", "timestamp": 1619339139, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1619349561, "url": "", "vote": {"vote_data": {"mac": 120, "win": 121, "围观": 159}, "vote_options": ["mac", "win", "围观"]}}}